arts.ttl: Girona to be without key player for remainder of 2024 as injury crisis continues
arts.sum: Girona have had rotten luck with injuries this season, and it has meant that they have struggled across all competitions – and especially in La Liga and the Champions League. Unfortunately, things are not exactly heading in the right direction either, as another key player was struck down during the international break. arts.ttl: When is Chile - Venezuela? how to watch on TV, stream online
arts.sum: The game between Chile - Venezuela will be played on Sunday November 19, with kick off at 7:00 p.m. ET / 4:00 p.m. PT. Chile looked better in their last game against Peru, where they had a good amount of chances to score.
